yle=\"color: red;\">冇被抄牌冇被拘留</span></strong></span>都會被點相，所以大家發夢萬事要小心謹慎呀！<br />\n                   <br />\n                              <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rT6Sax0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrT6Sax0.png&h=00cae3f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"係咪因為你後生？之前好似都有巴打講過澳門被人扣左幾個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n另外麻煩樓主幫手，正皮加推呢個，時間無多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出街全部對家街站，死得啦，麻煩認真幫推呢個整合左既行動PO啦，再唔做的野輸死喇：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【行動post】<span style=\"color: green;\">《緊急》全民選舉文宣+鍵盤戰</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743618</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原PO<br />\n選舉文宣！文宣！文宣呀！唔夠對家多呀！的牆無曬喇！</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezmgyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezmgyS</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"推了<br />\n應該唔係，我個fd同我差唔多年紀但佢冇事<br />\n衣着都應該唔關事，冇黑衫褲口罩，得頂黑帽"},{"pid":"21d67334b10ddad9e60b56bd8b690842297d4bfb","tid":1744280,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1f21f61f8a36a370838c585406282efc40b73cb","tid":1744280,"uid":140587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17e401127c1512ae7e79dea5edb38d61485eba9","tid":1744280,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3bed5f215f21f5e1280e50abf9317b66d7d0d32","tid":1744280,"uid":140587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"我知道依排仲去澳門嘅真係抵屌，對唔住咁多位手足<img src=\"/asset